---
<section class="bg-stone-50 py-14 md:py-20">
  <div class="container max-w-4xl text-center">
    <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight">Made by nature. Not a lab.</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Lab-made minerals and synthetic vitamins don't absorb the same way. Your body knows the difference.
      Purest uses only what nature already perfected — and nothing else.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <!-- Trace minerals -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 space-y-2 shadow-sm">
        <p class="font-serif text-3xl font-medium">85+</p>
        <p class="font-serif text-base font-medium">Trace Minerals</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">From natural sun-dried sea salt — including sodium, potassium, magnesium & more.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Sodium -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 space-y-2 shadow-sm">
        <p class="font-serif text-3xl font-medium">700+</p>
        <p class="font-serif text-base font-medium">mg Sodium</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Naturally occurring. No synthetic salt. No anti-caking agents. Ever.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Real fruit -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 space-y-2 shadow-sm">
        <p class="font-serif text-3xl font-medium">0</p>
        <p class="font-serif text-base font-medium">Added Sugar</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Zero added sugar. Zero maltodextrin. Just natural glucose from real freeze-dried fruit.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Ingredients -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 space-y-2 shadow-sm">
        <p class="font-serif text-3xl font-medium">Few</p>
        <p class="font-serif text-base font-medium">Ingredients</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">You can read every single one. If you can see it in the jar, it's in there. That's it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Nature vs Lab callout -->
    <div class="mt-10 bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm text-left max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <p class="font-serif text-xl tracking-tight">"If it's made in a lab, it doesn't work as well."</p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
        Synthetic vitamins and processed minerals create inflammation. Your gut doesn't recognize them.
        Purest is easy on your system because every ingredient comes directly from nature —
        the way your body was designed to absorb it.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-foreground/40 italic">— Pam Sweeney, Founder · Developed at 8,900 ft in Aspen, Colorado</p>
    </div>

    <a href="/products" class="mt-10 inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-foreground px-8 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-foreground hover:text-background transition-colors">
      Shop all flavors →
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
